Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19\fad(200,0)}（您有一条新消息）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  已经收拾的差不多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去一趟市政厅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去办迁户口的手续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  你今天要和夏海她们去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不是每天都约好出去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  偶尔也由你主动约她们一次如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}（今天有空吗？出去玩吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香会不会又做什么蠢事呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到短信  逢泽夏海（但为啥是来电 应该是动画作bug了）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  你现在在家里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香有没有打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没  出什么事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是旅游  大家一起去旅游吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是真正的巴厘岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早玩到晚的巴厘岛五日游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外国？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有护照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  随心所欲的冲绳三日游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕坐飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么北海道也不行了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢  成吉思汗锅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的预算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预支零花钱的话  大概2  3万
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概也就这点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐电车去不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗星卧铺特快？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么  电车？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个反而更贵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  纱季你尽是在发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么到底去哪里好  纱季想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我随便…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便才是最让人头疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去还在计划阶段就泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  京都？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有舞女体验  看上去好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就变成修学旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年不能一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想大家一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在那个时候回来一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经是决定好了的事  就不要再多提了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅游呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也决定不了去处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是大家一起去哪里玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里是指哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去纱季要搬去的地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去亲眼见证一下纱季的新家是怎么样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个人一起的修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错  真不错呢  东京  顺便观光一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴空塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Sky Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去武道馆  巨蛋也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是演唱会的会场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们去了我的新家也不会觉得多有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  不是挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去东京  东京  东京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是在东京  但其实是个小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐船要11个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是要去已经很麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在东京一个叫做竹芝的地方坐船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上出发早上才到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能订到船票呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我想预约几张船票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的  初中生四名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一股防虫剂的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不买新的不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你们要去小岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候转学我也觉得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是个好地方  你一定会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英语的作业你做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天轮到我上去讲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不是也会轮到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛你带字典了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香也没带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很重嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样  那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  老师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这梦是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱  要不要买呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试穿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不好意思  稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季不买吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  但看了就想买啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  晕车药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有晕电车和晕船用的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事要马上联系我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小岛如果纱季能喜欢上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会下雨吗  凛子你带伞了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的包也太小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说以防万一还是轻装上阵的好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岛上有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰熊之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说会稍微晚点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  真没办法  我先给你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指南？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  是纱季写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得一次的旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季从以前开始就很较真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞的像是真的修学旅行一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过亏了某个人的福  一上来行程稍微有点变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  抱歉  我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  下田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CD放在播放器里忘拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带来想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让大家一起听的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我存进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗  我要放了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是去一次九段下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（九段下: 武道馆所在地）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那么多钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是滨松町  滨松町  出口在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  船在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  是竹芝栈桥方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是东京塔  东京塔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我拍一张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京塔  和凛一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实也想多来这种地方看看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啊  我们又不是来观光的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么想去我的新家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说都会好奇吧  为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我也是第一次去  可没法保证那儿会有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  夏海  来拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要喊这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点  这么漂亮多拍几张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你悠闲地拍了那么多纪念照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  真大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去外面瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹桥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  东京
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有离开东京
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说船会摇得很厉害 但这完全没有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似出了东京湾就会摇得厉害了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了晕船药了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 优香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先要把行李安顿好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（免责声明 本次航程有可能无法到达目的地）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据情况  有可能会到不了那个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是如果浪太高  船就无法停泊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中途返回？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  我们的位子是最边上的两个和旁边的两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自的票上都写着号码吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛也要边上的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点 放好行李就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  像小孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜子里没有什么奇怪的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为还不到午夜零点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说  我不敢上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你按住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特等席是最好的席位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很厉害的人物在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去 会被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…纱季害怕被骂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  给你枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛也接着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不换上睡衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没换啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只把这个脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间用不着躲躲藏藏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让周围的人感到尴尬的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能躺下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了很多无用功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  夜晚才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是零食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外过夜是一定要吃夜宵的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  你不需要减肥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点  我费了很大劲带来的  吃啦吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是清汤口味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}给我一片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是特浓口味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 纱季 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到修学旅行的晚上就想到？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔枕头大战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨论恋爱话题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  纱季竟然说讨论恋爱话题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说  但其实？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说  但其实？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那夏海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你们看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客  马上就要到熄灯时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在本船正在东京湾内向着三宅岛航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外由于今天天气恶劣  海上浪高  预计船会摇得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议容易晕船的乘客及早就寝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然就熄灯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手机照一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吵到周围的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像只有我们四个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们在海上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越热了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  你刚才想拿什么出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水气球？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在找泳衣的时候发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前大家一起玩过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩过玩过  凛子是最擅长充水的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了岛上大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩  玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要玩  那就在找几个那里的小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  晕船了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找个塑料袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫乘务员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把船停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使停下来也是在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向神石许愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病也能治好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晕船不是病  说不定能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这太平洋上许愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英语作业做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天轮到我上去讲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  凛  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好上好  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带字典了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一会儿借给我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天放晴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才发现？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为之前一直都漆黑一片的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  你从下田出来的时候起就一直让人感觉很消沉似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有消沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:20:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想  这次是旅行  而下次再来就是搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不搬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就纱季一个人留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使就到上完初中为止也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以来我家住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去那个岛上的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸以前就说想在那个岛上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个愿望终于要达成了  所以非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人留下的话  这样太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没办法的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  又说没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季一直都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要自欺欺人  要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说没办法  然后就放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季说不出口的话  我去说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之后我去对叔叔说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他不要把纱季带走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  因为  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  不能吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我们没吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在哭吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候换的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有做准备运动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  你是这个岛上的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你们这群外地人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.66,0:23:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么嘛  那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  算什么嘛  那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味  岛上的寿司超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季要搬到这种地方来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.98,0:24:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 夏色奇迹 第九话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途的天空的尽头的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
